OL,3,CWelfare on the line as government
OL,4,Clooks for possible savings
OL,6,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,7,Fis drawing up plans to overhaul
OL,8,Fdisability and health benefits to
OL,9,Fsignificantly reduce the number of
OL,10,Fpeople who are judged as unable to
OL,11,Fwork.
OL,13,FThat means far fewer disabled people
OL,14,Fwill receive higher benefit levels,
OL,15,Fand many more will be expected to
OL,16,Fsearch for work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
