OL,3,CWelfare on the line as government
OL,4,Clooks for possible savings
OL,6,FThe changes to disability and health
OL,7,Fbenefits are being put forward in a
OL,8,Fgreen paper which is meant to be a way
OL,9,Fthat a government consults on
OL,10,Fproposals.
OL,12,FAs such, they were not meant to be
OL,13,Fscored in the spring statement. But
OL,14,FI've heard that's no longer the case -
OL,15,Fsome of the measures will be
OL,16,Fintroduced immediately so the savings
OL,17,Fcan be counted sooner.
