OL,3,CWelfare on the line as government
OL,4,Clooks for possible savings
OL,6,FThere will also be major changes to
OL,7,FPersonal Independence Payments - which
OL,8,Fare meant to help disabled people pay
OL,9,Ffor the additional costs associated
OL,10,Fwith their disability. The move is
OL,11,Flikely to trigger a major backlash.
OL,13,FI can also reveal that the previous
OL,14,FConservative prime minister Rishi
OL,15,FSunak stepped back from means testing
OL,16,FPersonal Independence Payments at the
OL,17,Flast moment after senior advisers
OL,18,Fwarned him that the optics would be
OL,19,Fterrible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
