OL,6,FAdvice, including written submissions,
OL,7,Fstressed that any changes would be
OL,8,Fseen as "taking wheelchairs and other
OL,9,Fessential aids" off a million disabled
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,FOn the suggestion that at least some
OL,13,Fdepartments had to identify 20% low
OL,14,Fpriority spending a Downing Street
OL,15,Fsource said it was certainly true that
OL,16,Fdepartments across government were
OL,17,Fbeing asked to "deprioritise" spending.
OL,19,FThey said that the state had ballooned
OL,20,Fand needed to be tackled.
