OL,6,FA Treasury source, however, said they
OL,7,Fdid not recognise the 20% figure.
OL,9,FThey said that departments had been
OL,10,Fasked to do a zero-based spending
OL,11,Freview going through spending
OL,12,Fdecisions line by line as the
OL,13,FChancellor searches for cuts.
OL,15,FSources from at least three
OL,16,Fdepartments told me about the 20%
OL,17,Ffigure, however.
