OL,11,FOn welfare, Sunak did push ahead with
OL,12,Fchanges to the work capability
OL,13,Fassessment- saying they would save
OL,14,F#3bn.
OL,16,FAdvisers saw them as much more
OL,17,Fpalatable for voters- with polls
OL,18,Fsuggesting people are quite
OL,19,Funsympathetic to those on out of work
OL,20,Fbenefits.
