OL,6,FBut his plan was challenged in the
OL,7,Fcourts and judges agreed with
OL,8,Fdisability campaigners that the
OL,9,Fconsultation had been misleading.
OL,11,FThe government suggested that the
OL,12,Fmotivation was not to save money but
OL,13,Fget people into work, but the OBR
OL,14,Fpredicted that while over 400,000
OL,15,Fwould lose money, only around 3,000
OL,16,Fwould move into jobs.
OL,18,FLabour accepts the consultation is
OL,19,Fflawed but is pushing ahead with cuts
OL,20,F- and much bigger than those
OL,21,Foriginally mooted.
